snippet.title: Numba Deluxe
snippet.description:
Create Numba chains in various sequences. Sound easy? Get ready for some great fun and absorbing game-play through 3 testing game modes as you strive to become the ultimate Numba Champion in this all-new puzzler.

Available for PC.
